{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BatSpawnInit}}
'''A_BatSpawnInit'''<br />
(no parameters)

Resets the calling actor's <tt>special1</tt> field to 0. This is used by the Hexen bat spawner to manage spawn frequency.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|BatSpawner}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Hexen functions]] [[Category:Decorate Status change functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:BatSpawnInit}}
